<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Wisdom_of_Crowds&action=edit&section=12.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Bikhchandani, Sushil, <a href="David_Hirshleifer" title="David Hirshleifer">David Hirshleifer</a>, and <a href="Ivo_Welch" title="Ivo Welch">Ivo Welch</a>. "A Theory of Fads, Fashion, Custom, and Cultural Change as <a href="Informational_Cascade" title="Informational Cascade" class="mw-redirect">Informational Cascades</a>." <i>Journal of Political Economy</i>, Vol. 100, No.5, pp.&#160;992–1026, 1992.</li>
